get.description:
通过WebSocket订阅指定交易对的K线数据
1. 客户端订阅请求格式:
{
"action": "subscribe",
"symbol": "AAPL",
"interval": "4h",
"type": 0
}
type说明: 0-股票, 1-加密货币, 2-外汇
2. 服务端响应格式:
连接成功:
{
"type": "connected",
"msg": "WebSocket connected successfully"
}
订阅确认:
{
"type": "subscribed",
"symbol": "AAPL",
"interval": "4h",
"msg": "Subscription updated"
}
K线更新:
{
"type": "kline_update",
"symbol": "AAPL",
"interval": "4h",
"data": {
"o": 150.25,
"h": 151.20,
"l": 149.80,
"c": 150.50,
"v": 1000000,
"t": 1683888999000
}
}

get.description:
建立WebSocket连接以接收实时价格推送
1. 客户端订阅请求格式:
{
"req": "symbols",
"symbols": ["AAPL","GOOGL"],
"type": 0
}
type说明: 0-股票, 1-加密货币, 2-外汇
2. 服务端响应格式:
连接成功:
{
"type": "connected",
"msg": "WebSocket connected successfully"
}
订阅确认:
{
"type": "subscribed",
"symbols": ["AAPL","GOOGL"],
"symbolType": "stock",
"msg": "Subscription updated"
}
价格更新:
{
"type": "price_update",
"data": {"AAPL": 150.25, "GOOGL": 2750.50},
"timestamp": 1683888999
}
